===== 1.0.0 =====
 * Initial Release

[...]

===== 1.4.0 =====
 * Added ability to export more variables in the tracking number: #d#, #m#, #Y#, #y# (Outputting the shipment date)

===== 1.4.1 =====
 + Added new variable #ORDERNUMBER#

===== 1.4.2 =====
 + Improved compatibility with not properly uninstalled shipping methods

===== 1.4.3 =====
 + Added new variables #FIRSTNAME# and #LASTNAME# that contain shipping first/lastname
 * Variables in tracking link get prepared using urlencode()

===== 1.4.4 =====
 + Added new variable #COUNTRYCODE# which contains the two letter destination country code